Package com.day.cq.mcm.campaign

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CallResults
    Represents the results of a call to a Adobe Campaign instance.
    CampaignConnector
    A service that is used to access a remote Adobe Campaign instance.
    GenericCampaignConnector
    A service that is used to access a remote Adobe Campaign instance.
    NewsletterStatus
    Reflects the current status of a newsletter.
    StatusService
    Service for retrieving the current status of a newsletter from a Adobe Campaign instance.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CampaignCredentials
    This class represents the credentials required for accessing a Adobe Campaign instance.
    Defs
    Defines some basic property names and other stuff used by the Adobe Campaign integration.
    RpcDefs
    Defines constants used for communicating with an Adobe Campaign instance.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ACConnectorException
    An exception that is thrown on errors accessing a Adobe Campaign instance
    CampaignException
    Base exception representing errors related to Adobe Campaign.
    ConfigurationException
    Thrown when the Adobe Campaign configuration is not present or invalid.
    ConnectionException
    Thrown when a connection to Adobe Campaign fails or returns with an unexpected status code.
